# Cloudflare Pages headers. https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
# Active-development policy: always revalidate so a new deploy is never masked by a
# stale browser cache. Browsers send a conditional request and get a fast 304 when
# nothing changed. Before scaling heavy paid traffic, consider switching JS/CSS to
# hashed filenames with long immutable caching for performance.

/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin

# Belt-and-suspenders: never cache the shared engine, config, or styles.
/funnel.js
  Cache-Control: no-cache
/verticals.js
  Cache-Control: no-cache
/styles.css
  Cache-Control: no-cache
